{"name":"Trapping","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-56976a83-7fff-5674-fe85-6827a739c7d1\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-289a35b2-7fff-8748-e029-9fbb0afbbd5b\">Use this to set and disarm traps. When setting traps Roll Under your Trapping Skill and describe how the trap is made with the materials at hand. When someone wishes to disarm a trap they must Roll Versus the original trap-setter&rsquo;s Trapping Skill. If the GM doesn&rsquo;t know what that <span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8b07cf47-7fff-b8d1-4ff0-82fa966bf7c1\">number should be assume 6 to be pretty simple while 12 is incredibly hard. Scale it between those as appropriate. </span></span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cF40jXjQ3ql3R4u4"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676781942840,"modifiedTime":1676782632708,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"4DPKyIK3IqggO6pw","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Disguise","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-56976a83-7fff-5674-fe85-6827a739c7d1\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3270f137-7fff-a5be-8ca9-e60768966dcf\">Covers the use of props to change your appearance. When in disguise you must Roll Under this when someone is liable to see through it. Opposed by Awareness when under scrutiny. </span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cF40jXjQ3ql3R4u4"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676781942840,"modifiedTime":1676782632706,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"4MzvyF4am3zl4Sis","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Climb","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-56976a83-7fff-5674-fe85-6827a739c7d1\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9608839-7fff-f7d9-ad08-dece9a7eb3af\">The usefulness of the ability to clamber up things cannot be overstated. Most climbs should be single rolls though longer or more difficult climbs may require multiple rolls. On these climbs consider requiring a number or total or repeated failures to fall off unless it is a particularly&nbsp; merciless ascent. The GM should use their discretion.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cF40jXjQ3ql3R4u4"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676781942840,"modifiedTime":1676782632706,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"4d7TsrdzvcBqtLvV","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Mathmology","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-56976a83-7fff-5674-fe85-6827a739c7d1\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8c1f86c7-7fff-f2b2-c206-da5cdb4f829d\">Use this to gain insight into angles, pressures, numbers, and other such arcane arts. You could, for instance, Test your Mathmology to get a good idea of the surface tension of a ball of inert plasmic goo or to find the fulcrum for tripping a giant.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cF40jXjQ3ql3R4u4"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676781942840,"modifiedTime":1676782632707,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"8pbumYSmJMvV1M3J","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Secret Signs","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-56976a83-7fff-5674-fe85-6827a739c7d1\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5ebd5f62-7fff-8a0d-912b-e28603b60d5f\">Used to identify marks, handshakes, code words, etc. of one specific society. You would, for example, be able to read the secret marks left on people&rsquo;s door posts by fellow hobos.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cF40jXjQ3ql3R4u4"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676781942840,"modifiedTime":1676782632708,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"Ayrtcghd9fXdsznV","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Poison","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-56976a83-7fff-5674-fe85-6827a739c7d1\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-937be9ec-7fff-4d9d-8833-0b842c0c9b48\">You may Test this Skill during down time to create a single dose of poison. Pick which kind it is when you make it. This list is not exhaustive &mdash; more exotic ones may be available if you possess the knowledge and ingredients. 1d3 Common Poisons of Troika: 1 Causes anyone ingesting it to Test their Luck (or Skill for Enemies) or lose 4d6 Stamina. 2 Add 1 to all Damage Rolls while this is applied to piercing or edged Weapons. If you Roll a 1 for Damage the poison has worn off. 3 Causes anyone ingesting it to fall unconscious for 1d6 hours. </span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cF40jXjQ3ql3R4u4"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676781942840,"modifiedTime":1676782632707,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"CbxqI1Q776xYksNg","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
